      {
        "Language": "ENG",
        "Name": "Heart of a Warrior",
        "Client": "Fugen the Elder",
        "Description": "Hey, Squirt! We\u0027ve got ourselves a little\r\nquest that\u0027ll determine who\u0027s the strongest\r\nhunter. My zenny\u0027s on you, but we\u0027ll see!\r\nAll ya gotta do is go and smack around\r\na Goss Harag and Magnamalo in the Arena\r\nand these titles are yours! Think you\u0027re up\r\nto it? Well go get to it! Bwahahaha!",
        "Target": "Hunt a Goss Harag and Magnamalo",
        "Fail": "Reward hits 0, or time expires"
      },
      {
        "Language": "FRE",
        "Name": "C\u0153ur vaillant",
        "Client": "Fugen l\u0027Ancien",
        "Description": "H\u00E9, voici la qu\u00EAte parfaite pour\r\nd\u00E9terminer qui est le meilleur\r\nchasseur. Je parie sur toi, on verra\r\nbien ! T\u0027as juste \u00E0 zigouiller un\r\nGoss Harag et Magnamalo dans l\u0027Ar\u00E8ne\r\npour remporter le titre ! Tu penses\r\n\u00EAtre de taille ?! Allez, au boulot !",
